  "detailed_description": "Welcome to a world where speed and strategy combine in unforgettable competitions! Saddle up your giant bird and race along looping routes filled with unexpected obstacles and opportunities to overtake. Outsmart your opponents, use tactics and various tools to get ahead. Ready to take on the challenge and become a legend of these extreme races? <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3130960/extras/24934cdf356c8677321287df580857bd.webp?t=1740147640\" width=616 height=25 /></span><br><strong>Outrun rivals in dynamic races on giant birds</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3130960/extras/08d4f15d3a59b1f81595516b6b57f658.poster.avif?t=1740147640\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3130960/extras/08d4f15d3a59b1f81595516b6b57f658.webm?t=1740147640\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3130960/extras/08d4f15d3a59b1f81595516b6b57f658.mp4?t=1740147640\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Immerse yourself in a world of fast-paced competition! Overcome unique tracks in diverse locations, dodge obstacles, and shoot accurately at targets to earn extra points. Feel the adrenaline in single-player or compete with friends in exciting multiplayer modes. <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3130960/extras/24934cdf356c8677321287df580857bd.webp?t=1740147640\" width=616 height=25 /></span><br><strong>Use every tool for victory</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3130960/extras/812ed2c6dc2f5731e179a028467cd147.poster.avif?t=1740147640\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3130960/extras/812ed2c6dc2f5731e179a028467cd147.webm?t=1740147640\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3130960/extras/812ed2c6dc2f5731e179a028467cd147.mp4?t=1740147640\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>There are no rules in the race for first place! Shoot with a gun, hit with a stick, use a whip, or throw a rope with stones to slow down your rivals. Show tactical skill and cunning to overtake everyone and cross the finish line first. <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3130960/extras/24934cdf356c8677321287df580857bd.webp?t=1740147640\" width=616 height=25 /></span><br><strong>Express your unique style through customization</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3130960/extras/0b62289f1732339c4d235d648853adcd.poster.avif?t=1740147640\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3130960/extras/0b62289f1732339c4d235d648853adcd.webm?t=1740147640\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3130960/extras/0b62289f1732339c4d235d648853adcd.mp4?t=1740147640\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Make your character stand out with extensive customization options. Choose from a variety of outfits and accessories for yourself and your bird to shine on the track and emphasize your individuality. <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3130960/extras/24934cdf356c8677321287df580857bd.webp?t=1740147640\" width=616 height=25 /></span>",
